Support for iOS 15 and watchOS 8. Improved the transcription process. Hear VoiceOver through a headset while recording from the internal mic. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Added a button to skip forward. Added the option to adjust the speed of saved audio. Fixed problem with auto splitting. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Fixed problem with auto splitting. Memos in the trash can are now deleted after 30 days. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Automatic transcription of memos. Use a widget to quickly start recording. Directly view progress of downloads uploads and compressions. Rename memos on Apple Watch. Add position markers while recording on Apple Watch. Memos are compressed while recording. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Send memos by email without size restrictions except the ones from email providers . Improved connections with https: imesart.com connect.php. More space for list of memos on iPad. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Encrypt memos sent to cloud services. Faster app startup. Fixed quality issues when playing back to some Bluetooth devices. Fixed use of complications on some Series 2 and 3 watches. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Added support for sending to SharePoint. Fixed connection problems with OneDrive. Fixed upload problem with some WebDAV servers. Fixed reconnection problem with SFTP servers. Added support for all complications of Apple Watch Series 4. Added background recording under watchOS 5. Many other improvements. Encrypt memos sent by email. Improved support of Bluetooth and AirPlay devices. Improved remote control from Apple Watch. Copy a memo by making a long press on it in the list of memos. Fixed crash that stopped recording for some users under iOS 11. Record button is once again easily accessible with VoiceOver. Added support for Drag and Drop. Fixed Pause Play button on lock screen. Fixes random crash shortly after playback stopped under iOS 11. Much faster to start playing or recording under iOS 11. Fixed a bug that prevented playback until the app restarted.
